    ['Specialized Tarmac SL8 Comp', 'Cycling', 4500.00, 'Specialized Tarmac SL8 Comp is the race bike that won the Tour de France. Full FACT 10r carbon frame weighs just 795g. Shimano 105 Di2 12-speed electronic shifting delivers pro-level precision. DT Swiss R470 wheels with 28mm Turbo Cotton tires balance speed and comfort. Integrated cockpit with hidden cables for aerodynamic efficiency. Rider-First Engineered sizing ensures identical ride quality across all sizes. Power Saddle included. Complete bike weight: 7.9 kg.', ['brand' => 'Specialized', 'color' => 'Gloss Black', 'material' => 'Carbon']],
    ['Wahoo KICKR V6 Smart Trainer', 'Cycling', 1299.99, 'Wahoo KICKR V6 is the gold standard indoor smart trainer. Electromagnetic resistance unit simulates up to 26% gradient with 2200W max power. ±1% power accuracy — no calibration needed. Dual-band ANT+/Bluetooth connects to Zwift, TrainerRoad, and all major apps. KICKR AXIS feet add natural side-to-side movement for realistic ride feel. Integrated cadence sensor. Whisper-quiet direct drive. Auto-calibrates via WiFi firmware updates. Compatible with 8-12 speed cassettes (11-speed included). Foldable legs for compact storage.', ['brand' => 'Wahoo', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Giro Aether MIPS Helmet', 'Cycling', 299.99, 'Giro Aether Spherical helmet combines safety, comfort, and ventilation. MIPS Spherical technology uses two shell layers that rotate independently to redirect rotational energy in a crash. 21 wind tunnel-optimized vents channel air across your head. Roc Loc 5+ Air fit system adjusts in three dimensions with a single hand. Ionic+ antimicrobial padding stays fresh. 260g featherweight construction. Meets CPSC, CE EN1078, and AS/NZS 2063 safety standards. Magnetic Fidlock buckle opens with one hand.', ['brand' => 'Giro', 'color' => 'Matte White']],

    // ===== Sports & Outdoors > Running =====
    ['Nike Alphafly 3', 'Running', 284.99, 'Nike Alphafly 3 is the record-breaking marathon super shoe. Full-length ZoomX foam provides maximum energy return. Dual Air Zoom units under the forefoot launch you forward with every stride. Carbon fiber flyplate adds propulsive snap. Atomknit 3.0 upper breathes while providing structure. 39.5mm stack height stays within World Athletics regulations. Designed for race day — from 5K to marathon distance. Slightly curved forefoot geometry promotes smooth, efficient toe-off. 220g weight (men\'s size 10).', ['brand' => 'Nike', 'color' => 'Volt/Black']],
    ['ASICS Gel-Kayano 31', 'Running', 189.99, 'ASICS Gel-Kayano 31 is the premium stability running shoe for overpronators. FF Blast Plus ECO cushioning uses 24% bio-based content for a softer, lighter ride. 4D Guidance System provides smooth support without restricting natural foot movement. PureGEL technology in the heel absorbs impact at footstrike. AHARPLUS outsole rubber extends durability in high-wear areas. Engineered mesh upper with internal support structure. OrthoLite X-55 sockliner for step-in comfort. Ideal for daily training and long runs.', ['brand' => 'ASICS', 'color' => 'French Blue/Electric Lime']],
    ['Hoka Clifton 9', 'Running', 144.99, 'Hoka Clifton 9 delivers a smooth, lightweight ride for everyday runners. Compression-molded EVA midsole provides plush cushioning at only 248g. Early-stage Meta-Rocker geometry promotes a smooth, efficient stride. Breathable engineered mesh upper with yarn overlays for structure. Extended heel crash pad absorbs impact. Durabrasion rubber outsole in key areas for longevity. Flat-waisted geometry increases ground contact for stability. Reflective details for low-light visibility. A versatile shoe for easy runs, recovery days, and standing all day.', ['brand' => 'Hoka', 'color' => 'Black/White']],
    ['Garmin HRM-Pro Plus Chest Strap', 'Running', 129.99, 'Garmin HRM-Pro Plus is the premium chest strap heart rate monitor for serious athletes. Dual transmission broadcasts simultaneously via ANT+ and Bluetooth to your watch, phone, and gym equipment. Stores and syncs offline running dynamics: vertical oscillation, ground contact time, stride length, vertical ratio. Swimming-capable with pool heart rate storage. Soft, adjustable strap with non-slip silicone grip. CR2032 battery lasts up to 1 year. Compatible with all Garmin watches, Peloton, Zwift, and other Bluetooth fitness apps.', ['brand' => 'Garmin', 'color' => 'Black']],

    // ===== Books > Fiction =====
    ['Dune by Frank Herbert', 'Fiction', 16.99, 'Frank Herbert\'s Dune is the bestselling science fiction novel of all time and the basis for the blockbuster films. Set on the desert planet Arrakis, the story follows young Paul Atreides as his family takes control of the most valuable resource in the universe: the spice melange. A sweeping tale of politics, religion, ecology, and human potential. Herbert created one of literature\'s most complete and immersive fictional worlds, influencing everything from Star Wars to Game of Thrones. This edition includes the complete, unabridged text with a new introduction.', ['brand' => 'Penguin Books']],
    ['Project Hail Mary by Andy Weir', 'Fiction', 14.99, 'From the author of The Martian comes another gripping survival story set in space. Ryland Grace wakes up alone on a spaceship with no memory of who he is or why he\'s there. He\'s the sole survivor of a last-chance mission to save Earth from an extinction-level threat. As his memories return, he discovers the nature of his desperate quest and forms an unlikely alliance. Filled with science, humor, and heart, Project Hail Mary is a celebration of human ingenuity and the universal desire for connection. Hardcover, 496 pages.', ['brand' => 'Ballantine Books']],
    ['The Midnight Library by Matt Haig', 'Fiction', 13.99, 'Between life and death there is a library, and within that library, the shelves go on forever. Every book provides a chance to try another life you could have lived. Nora Seed finds herself in the Midnight Library, where she can undo every regret and try out different versions of her life. A librarian guides her through the infinite possibilities. But things aren\'t always what they seem. A beautiful, uplifting novel about the choices that make us who we are. International bestseller translated into 40+ languages. Paperback, 304 pages.', ['brand' => 'Penguin Books']],
    ['Klara and the Sun by Kazuo Ishiguro', 'Fiction', 15.99, 'Nobel Prize-winning author Kazuo Ishiguro tells the story of Klara, an Artificial Friend with outstanding observational qualities, who watches customers from her place in a store, hoping to be chosen. When she is selected by Josie, a sickly teenager, Klara is determined to learn everything about the human heart. A masterful exploration of love, sacrifice, and what it means to be human — told from the perspective of an AI. Haunting and deeply moving. Paperback, 320 pages.', ['brand' => 'Vintage Books']],
    ['Babel by R.F. Kuang', 'Fiction', 17.99, 'Babel, Or the Necessity of Violence: An Arcane History of the Oxford Translators\' Revolution. Set in an alternate 1830s Oxford, Robin Swift is brought from Canton to study at the prestigious Royal Institute of Translation — known as Babel. There, the brightest minds translate ancient texts to power the British Empire through silver-working: a magical craft that harnesses the lost meanings between languages. Robin must choose between the empire that raised him and the homeland it exploits. Dark academia meets anti-colonial fantasy. Hardcover, 560 pages.', ['brand' => 'Harper Voyager']],

    // ===== Books > Non-Fiction =====
    ['Atomic Habits by James Clear', 'Non-Fiction', 11.99, 'Atomic Habits by James Clear reveals how tiny changes in behavior can lead to remarkable results. Drawing on biology, psychology, and neuroscience, Clear demonstrates that the key to lasting change isn\'t one massive transformation but rather small, compounding improvements — just 1% better each day. The Four Laws of Behavior Change provide a framework for building good habits and breaking bad ones. Includes practical strategies for: habit stacking, temptation bundling, the two-minute rule, and environment design. #1 New York Times bestseller with 15+ million copies sold.', ['brand' => 'Avery']],
    ['Sapiens: A Brief History of Humankind', 'Non-Fiction', 14.99, 'Yuval Noah Harari\'s Sapiens explores how Homo sapiens came to dominate the planet. From the Cognitive Revolution 70,000 years ago to the biotechnology revolution of the 21st century, Harari examines how biology and history have defined what it means to be human. Why did our species succeed while other human species failed? How did money, empires, and religion come to unite billions? A thought-provoking journey through the entire history of humankind. Translated into 65 languages with 25+ million copies sold worldwide.', ['brand' => 'Harper Perennial']],
    ['Thinking, Fast and Slow by Daniel Kahneman', 'Non-Fiction', 13.99, 'Nobel Prize winner Daniel Kahneman takes readers on a groundbreaking tour of the mind. He reveals the two systems that drive the way we think: System 1, which is fast, intuitive, and emotional; and System 2, which is slower, more deliberative, and more logical. Kahneman exposes the extraordinary capabilities and faults of fast thinking, and the pervasive influence of intuitive impressions on our thoughts and behavior. Includes insights on: cognitive biases, prospect theory, the planning fallacy, and the illusion of understanding. Essential reading for anyone who thinks.', ['brand' => 'Farrar, Straus and Giroux']],

    // ===== Books > Technical =====
    ['Designing Data-Intensive Applications', 'Technical', 44.99, 'Martin Kleppmann\'s comprehensive guide to the big ideas behind reliable, scalable, and maintainable data systems. Covers: database internals (B-Trees, LSM-Trees, column storage), replication and partitioning strategies, consistency and consensus protocols, stream and batch processing, and the future of data systems. Practical examples from real systems: PostgreSQL, Cassandra, Kafka, Spark, Flink. Essential reading for software engineers, architects, and technical managers working with data at any scale. O\'Reilly Media, 616 pages.', ['brand' => "O'Reilly Media"]],
    ['Clean Code by Robert C. Martin', 'Technical', 39.99, 'Clean Code teaches the principles, patterns, and practices of writing clean, readable code. Uncle Bob Martin and his colleagues share their best agile practices of cleaning code on the fly. Real-world case studies progressively improve code — transforming messy functions, classes, and modules into clean, professional work. Covers: meaningful names, functions, comments, formatting, error handling, unit tests, classes, and systems. Every programmer should read this at least once. Even if you disagree with some principles, it will make you think more carefully about your craft. Prentice Hall, 464 pages.', ['brand' => 'Prentice Hall']],
    ['System Design Interview Vol. 1', 'Technical', 35.99, 'Alex Xu\'s System Design Interview is the practical guide to acing technical interviews and building scalable systems. Step-by-step frameworks for designing: URL shorteners, web crawlers, notification systems, news feeds, chat systems, and more. Each chapter walks through: requirements gathering, high-level design, deep dive into components, and scaling considerations. Covers: load balancing, caching, database sharding, message queues, rate limiters, consistent hashing. Used by engineers at Google, Meta, Amazon, and Microsoft for interview preparation. Self-published, 320 pages.', ['brand' => 'Byte Code LLC']],

    // ===== Books > Children =====
    ['The Very Hungry Caterpillar', 'Children', 8.99, 'Eric Carle\'s beloved classic has been charming readers for over 55 years. Follow a tiny caterpillar as he eats his way through an increasingly large amount of food before transforming into a beautiful butterfly. The innovative die-cut pages let little fingers explore the holes the caterpillar made. Teaches counting, days of the week, healthy eating, and the life cycle of a butterfly — all through a simple, joyful story. Board book edition with sturdy pages perfect for babies and toddlers. Translated into 70+ languages with 55+ million copies sold.', ['brand' => 'Philomel Books']],
    ['Where the Wild Things Are', 'Children', 9.99, 'Maurice Sendak\'s Caldecott Medal-winning picture book about Max, a mischievous boy sent to bed without supper, whose bedroom transforms into a wild jungle. He sails to the land of the Wild Things, becomes their king, and leads a wild rumpus. But eventually Max smells good things to eat and wants to be where someone loves him best of all. A timeless story about imagination, emotions, and the comfort of home. The illustrations are among the most recognized in children\'s literature. Hardcover, 48 pages.', ['brand' => 'HarperCollins']],

    // ===== Beauty & Health > Skincare =====
    ['CeraVe Moisturizing Cream 539g', 'Skincare', 18.99, 'CeraVe Moisturizing Cream is the dermatologist-recommended body and face moisturizer for dry to very dry skin. Contains three essential ceramides (1, 3, 6-II) that restore and maintain the skin\'s natural protective barrier. MVE Technology provides 24-hour hydration with a controlled release of ceramides and hyaluronic acid. Fragrance-free, non-comedogenic, and allergy-tested. Rich, non-greasy texture absorbs quickly. Accepted by the National Eczema Association. Developed with dermatologists. The 539g tub size lasts months with daily use.', ['brand' => 'CeraVe']],
    ['The Ordinary Niacinamide 10% + Zinc 1%', 'Skincare', 5.90, 'The Ordinary Niacinamide 10% + Zinc 1% is the cult-favorite serum that targets blemishes and congestion. High-concentration niacinamide (vitamin B3) helps reduce the appearance of enlarged pores and uneven skin tone. Zinc PCA balances oil production and soothes irritation. Water-based, oil-free formula layers perfectly under moisturizer and sunscreen. Vegan, cruelty-free, and free from alcohol, silicones, and sulfates. Part of The Ordinary\'s mission to bring effective skincare at honest prices. 30ml dropper bottle.', ['brand' => 'The Ordinary']],
    ['La Roche-Posay Anthelios SPF 50+', 'Skincare', 29.99, 'La Roche-Posay Anthelios UVMune 400 Invisible Fluid SPF 50+ is the gold standard of European sun protection. Exclusive Mexoryl 400 filter provides superior UVA protection at the critical 400nm wavelength — where other sunscreens fall short. Ultra-lightweight fluid texture absorbs instantly with no white cast on any skin tone. Water-resistant for 80 minutes. Non-comedogenic and suitable for sensitive skin. Fragrance-free. Tested under dermatological control. 50ml. Apply generously 15 minutes before sun exposure.', ['brand' => 'La Roche-Posay']],
    ['Paula\'s Choice 2% BHA Liquid Exfoliant', 'Skincare', 32.00, 'Paula\'s Choice Skin Perfecting 2% BHA Liquid Exfoliant is the global bestseller that transformed the skincare industry. Salicylic acid (BHA) penetrates pores to dissolve trapped sebum and dead skin cells, reducing blackheads and breakouts. Green tea extract provides antioxidant protection. Gentle enough for daily use — no harsh scrubbing or redness. Non-abrasive and fragrance-free. Apply with a cotton pad after cleansing. Visible results in as little as one week: smoother texture, smaller pores, clearer skin. 118ml bottle.', ['brand' => "Paula's Choice"]],

    // ===== Beauty & Health > Haircare =====
    ['Dyson Airwrap Multi-Styler', 'Haircare', 599.99, 'Dyson Airwrap uses the Coanda effect — no extreme heat required. Engineered to curl, wave, smooth, and dry with air, not extreme heat damage. Six attachments included: 30mm and 40mm barrels for curls and waves, smoothing dryer, round volumizing brush, firm smoothing brush, and coanda smoothing dryer. Intelligent heat control measures temperature 40 times per second to prevent damage. Three speed settings and three heat settings. Works on all hair types. Enhanced Coanda airflow in the latest model provides better styling with less frizz.', ['brand' => 'Dyson', 'color' => 'Nickel/Copper']],
    ['Olaplex No. 3 Hair Perfector', 'Haircare', 30.00, 'Olaplex No. 3 Hair Perfector is the at-home bond-building treatment that repairs damaged hair from the inside out. Patented bis-aminopropyl diglycol dimaleate works on a molecular level to relink broken disulfide bonds caused by chemical, thermal, and mechanical damage. Apply to damp hair, leave for 10+ minutes, then shampoo and condition. Results after first use: reduced breakage, improved shine, smoother texture, and more vibrant color. Vegan, cruelty-free, sulfate-free, and paraben-free. 100ml treatment lasts 8-12 uses.', ['brand' => 'Olaplex']],
    ['Moroccanoil Treatment Original', 'Haircare', 48.00, 'Moroccanoil Treatment is the versatile argan oil-infused hair treatment that started the oil-based hair care revolution. Conditions, detangles, and speeds up drying time. Rich in antioxidant-filled argan oil, vitamins, and proteins. Apply to damp hair before styling or dry hair for a finishing touch. Absorbs instantly without greasy residue. Tames frizz in any humidity. Provides UV protection. Signature Moroccanoil scent with notes of amber and musk. For all hair types and textures. 100ml with pump. Also available in Light formula for fine hair.', ['brand' => 'Moroccanoil']],

    // ===== Beauty & Health > Supplements =====
    ['Athletic Greens AG1', 'Supplements', 79.00, 'AG1 by Athletic Greens is the comprehensive daily nutritional supplement trusted by health experts. 75 vitamins, minerals, and whole-food sourced ingredients in one scoop. Supports gut health with prebiotics, probiotics, and digestive enzymes. Adaptogens for stress management. Antioxidants for immune support. NSF Certified for Sport — trusted by professional athletes. Third-party tested for purity and potency. Mix one scoop with cold water each morning. Pineapple-vanilla flavor with no artificial sweeteners. 30-serving pouch with a 60-day money-back guarantee.', ['brand' => 'Athletic Greens']],
    ['Creatine Monohydrate by Thorne', 'Supplements', 32.00, 'Thorne Creatine is NSF Certified for Sport pure creatine monohydrate. Supports muscle endurance, power output, and lean body mass. Also supports cognitive function and cellular energy production. Micronized for better solubility and absorption — mixes easily in water or smoothies. 5g per scoop, unflavored. No artificial sweeteners, fillers, or additives. 90 servings per container. Thorne products are used by 100+ professional sports teams and trusted by Mayo Clinic. Third-party tested and GMP certified. Take daily for cumulative benefits.', ['brand' => 'Thorne']],

    // ===== Beauty & Health > Tools =====
    ['Philips Sonicare DiamondClean 9900', 'Tools', 329.99, 'Philips Sonicare DiamondClean 9900 Prestige is the most advanced electric toothbrush. SenseIQ technology adapts brushing power, motion, and intensity in real-time based on your technique and pressure. 62,000 brush strokes per minute with patented sonic technology. Pressure sensor with gentle pulse alert. 4 brushing modes: Clean, Deep Clean+, Gum Health, and Sensitive. A-shaped premium brush head removes up to 20x more plaque than manual brushing. Wireless charging travel case with USB-C. 14-day battery life. Connected to Sonicare app for personalized coaching.', ['brand' => 'Philips', 'color' => 'Midnight Blue']],
    ['Foreo Luna 4', 'Tools', 279.00, 'FOREO LUNA 4 is the smart facial cleansing and firming device that replaced your washcloth. T-Sonic pulsations at 8000 RPM remove 99.5% of dirt, oil, and makeup residue in 60 seconds. Silicone touchpoints are 35x more hygienic than nylon bristle brushes. Firming mode tightens and tones facial muscles. App-connected with personalized routines. Waterproof IPX7 for shower use. Medical-grade silicone is gentle on sensitive skin. One charge lasts 4 months via USB-C. 2-year warranty. Replaces annual spend on disposable cleansing tools.', ['brand' => 'FOREO', 'color' => 'Lavender']],

    // ===== Toys & Games > Board Games =====
    ['Catan Board Game', 'Board Games', 44.99, 'Catan is the award-winning strategy board game that launched the modern board game renaissance. Players collect and trade resources — lumber, brick, wool, grain, and ore — to build roads, settlements, and cities on the island of Catan. Every game creates a unique board layout for endless replayability. Intuitive yet deep mechanics reward both negotiation skills and strategic planning. 3-4 players, ages 10+, 60-120 minute games. Over 40 million copies sold worldwide. Winner of the Spiel des Jahres (Game of the Year). Expandable with 5-6 player extension.', ['brand' => 'Catan Studio']],
    ['Wingspan Board Game', 'Board Games', 59.99, 'Wingspan is the critically acclaimed engine-building board game about birds. As a bird enthusiast, attract a beautiful and diverse collection of birds to your wildlife preserves. Each of the 170 unique bird cards is powered by a real bird\'s actual traits and behaviors. Collect eggs, cache food, and build an interconnected engine of bird powers. Gorgeous artwork by Natalia Rojas and Ana Maria Martinez Jaramillo. 1-5 players, ages 10+, 40-70 minutes. Winner of the 2019 Kennerspiel des Jahres. Includes eggs, food tokens, bird feeder dice tower, and more.', ['brand' => 'Stonemaier Games']],
    ['Pandemic Board Game', 'Board Games', 39.99, 'Pandemic is the cooperative board game where players work together as disease-fighting specialists to save the world. Four deadly diseases are spreading across the globe — your team must discover cures before outbreaks overwhelm humanity. Each player has a unique role: Medic, Scientist, Researcher, Dispatcher, or Operations Expert. Coordinate actions, share knowledge, and manage crises as a team. Win together or lose together. 2-4 players, ages 8+, 45-minute games. One of the most influential cooperative games ever designed. Spawned multiple expansions and legacy versions.', ['brand' => 'Z-Man Games']],
    ['Ticket to Ride', 'Board Games', 49.99, 'Ticket to Ride is the cross-country train adventure board game that\'s easy to learn and endlessly fun. Collect colored train cards to claim railway routes connecting cities across North America. Longer routes score more points, but watch out — rivals might block your path. Complete secret Destination Tickets for bonus points. Simple card-collection mechanics make it accessible to non-gamers. 2-5 players, ages 8+, 30-60 minutes. Over 10 million copies sold. Winner of multiple awards including Spiel des Jahres. Numerous map expansions available.', ['brand' => 'Days of Wonder']],

    // ===== Toys & Games > Puzzles =====
    ['LEGO Architecture Eiffel Tower 10307', 'Puzzles', 629.99, 'LEGO Architecture Eiffel Tower is the ultimate building experience at 1.5 meters tall. 10,001 pieces recreate Paris\'s most iconic landmark in stunning detail. Four curved legs with authentic lattice metalwork converge to the observation deck and antenna. Accurate proportions and intricate cross-bracing reflect Gustave Eiffel\'s 1889 engineering marvel. Includes a nameplate with facts. Display piece stands 149 cm tall on a built base representing the Champ de Mars. Ages 18+. Approximately 20+ hours of focused building. The tallest LEGO set ever produced.', ['brand' => 'LEGO']],
    ['Ravensburger Gradient 1000pc Puzzle', 'Puzzles', 17.99, 'Ravensburger Gradient 1000-piece puzzle is a mesmerizing challenge of pure color. 1000 pieces transition smoothly through the entire visible color spectrum — from deep red through orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, and violet. No image reference to rely on — only your eye for subtle color differences. Ravensburger\'s SoftClick Technology ensures a tight, satisfying fit with no false matches. Premium linen-structured surface reduces glare. Finished size: 70x50 cm. Made from recycled materials. Perfect for meditation, mindfulness, and screen-free evenings.', ['brand' => 'Ravensburger']],
    ['Rubik\'s Cube 3x3 Speed Cube', 'Puzzles', 12.99, 'The official Rubik\'s Speed Cube 3x3 is redesigned for competitive speedcubing. Smooth, fast corner cutting allows aggressive turning without lockups. Spring-tension mechanism is adjustable for your preferred feel. Stickerless design with embedded colored tiles that never peel or fade. 56mm competition size meets WCA (World Cube Association) standards. Lubricant-ready for even faster times. Includes cube stand for display. Over 43 quintillion possible combinations, one solution. The world record is under 3.5 seconds — how fast can you go?', ['brand' => "Rubik's"]],

    // ===== Toys & Games > Outdoor Toys =====
    ['Razor A5 Lux Kick Scooter', 'Outdoor Toys', 109.99, 'Razor A5 Lux is the premium kick scooter for kids and adults. Extra-large 200mm urethane wheels provide a smooth, stable ride on sidewalks and streets. Adjustable handlebars extend from 68 to 106 cm for riders of all heights. Rear fender brake for quick, controlled stops. Aircraft-grade aluminum T-tube and deck keep weight at just 3.6 kg. Folds flat in seconds for carrying and storage. Anti-rattle folding mechanism eliminates wobble. Weight capacity: 100 kg. Perfect for commuting, campus, or neighborhood cruising. Ages 8+.', ['brand' => 'Razor', 'color' => 'Blue']],
    ['Nerf Elite 2.0 Eaglepoint RD-8', 'Outdoor Toys', 29.99, 'Nerf Elite 2.0 Eaglepoint RD-8 is the tactical bolt-action blaster for aspiring sharpshooters. 8-dart rotating drum fires darts one at a time with satisfying bolt-action priming. Detachable scope for aiming accuracy. Tactical rails for customizing with Nerf accessories. Fires darts up to 27 meters. Includes 16 Official Nerf Elite 2.0 darts. Pull back the bolt, line up your shot through the scope, and fire. The bolt-action mechanism adds realism and encourages deliberate, accurate play. Ages 8+. No batteries required.', ['brand' => 'Nerf']],

    // ===== Toys & Games > Educational =====
    ['Osmo Genius Starter Kit for iPad', 'Educational', 99.99, 'Osmo Genius Starter Kit combines physical play with digital learning through AI-powered visual recognition. Place real objects in front of your iPad — Osmo sees them through the camera and responds on screen. Five award-winning games included: Numbers (math), Tangram (spatial reasoning), Words (spelling), Newton (physics), and Masterpiece (drawing). Ages 6-10. Adaptive difficulty grows with your child. Includes Osmo Base for iPad, tangram pieces, and letter tiles. STEM + Creativity in one system. Compatible with iPad 2+ and iPad mini. No internet required during play.', ['brand' => 'Osmo']],
    ['National Geographic Mega Fossil Dig Kit', 'Educational', 29.99, 'National Geographic Mega Fossil Dig Kit lets young paleontologists excavate 15 real fossils from a large excavation brick. Specimens include: shark teeth, brachiopods, ammonites, fish vertebrae, and more — all millions of years old. Full-color learning guide identifies each fossil with scientific facts and historical context. Includes excavation tools: chisel, brush, and magnifying glass. Teaches patience, scientific methodology, and geological history. Ages 8+. All specimens are ethically and responsibly sourced. Each fossil is unique. Perfect rainy-day activity.', ['brand' => 'National Geographic']],
    ['Snap Circuits Pro SC-500', 'Educational', 74.99, 'Snap Circuits Pro SC-500 teaches electronics through 500+ projects that kids build themselves. No soldering or tools required — color-coded components snap together on a grid. Build: working AM/FM radios, burglar alarms, doorbells, digital voice recorders, and more. 75+ components including: resistors, capacitors, transistors, ICs, LEDs, motors, speakers, and a photoresistor. Full-color illustrated manual with step-by-step instructions. Teaches real circuit fundamentals used in engineering. Ages 8+. Winner of numerous toy industry awards. Compatible with Snap Circuits expansion kits.', ['brand' => 'Elenco']],

    // ===== Clothing > Men =====
    ['Patagonia Better Sweater Fleece Jacket', 'Men', 139.00, 'Patagonia Better Sweater is the go-anywhere fleece jacket that looks as good in the office as on the trail. Made from 100% recycled polyester knit fleece that mimics the look of a wool sweater. Full-zip design with stand-up collar and raglan sleeves for mobility. Offset zipper garage prevents chin chafe. Zippered handwarmer and chest pockets. Fair Trade Certified sewn. Hip length sits above the harness for climbing. Machine washable. 370g weight. Available in Regular and Tall. Part of Patagonia\'s commitment to environmental responsibility.', ['brand' => 'Patagonia', 'color' => 'New Navy', 'material' => 'Recycled Polyester']],
    ['Uniqlo Ultra Light Down Jacket', 'Men', 79.90, 'Uniqlo Ultra Light Down Jacket is the featherweight layer you\'ll wear from autumn through spring. Premium 90% down fill provides warmth without bulk — packs into its own carrying pouch the size of a water bottle. Water-repellent nylon outer shell sheds light rain. Collarless design layers seamlessly under a blazer or coat. Elastic binding at cuffs and hem seal in warmth. 188g total weight (size M). Inner chest pocket doubles as storage pouch. Machine washable. Available in 15+ colors. The essential travel companion.', ['brand' => 'Uniqlo', 'color' => 'Dark Green', 'material' => 'Nylon/Down']],
    ['Levi\'s 501 Original Fit Jeans', 'Men', 69.50, 'Levi\'s 501 Original Fit Jeans are the icon that started it all in 1873. Straight leg, button fly, and a fit that sits at the waist. 12.5 oz non-stretch denim that molds to your body over time — no two pairs age the same way. The original riveted jean that miners, rebels, presidents, and rock stars have all worn. Medium Stonewash colorway delivers that perfectly broken-in look from day one. 100% cotton. Five-pocket styling. Belt loops. Levi\'s Red Tab. Made with Water<Less finishing that saves up to 96% of water in the finishing process.', ['brand' => "Levi's", 'color' => 'Medium Stonewash', 'material' => 'Cotton Denim']],
    ['Arc\'teryx Atom Hoody', 'Men', 300.00, 'Arc\'teryx Atom Hoody is the versatile synthetic insulated jacket for active use in cool conditions. Coreloft Compact insulation retains warmth even when wet — unlike down. Breathable, stretch side panels allow unrestricted movement and regulate temperature during aerobic activities. Insulated StormHood fits under a helmet. Durable, wind-resistant Tyono 20 face fabric. Elastic cuffs and adjustable hem. Two zippered hand pockets and one internal pocket. 375g. The Atom is the do-everything midlayer for climbing, skiing, hiking, and daily wear in unpredictable weather.', ['brand' => "Arc'teryx", 'color' => 'Black Sapphire', 'material' => 'Nylon/Coreloft']],

    // ===== Clothing > Women =====
    ['Lululemon Align High-Rise Pant 25"', 'Women', 98.00, 'Lululemon Align pants are the buttery-soft leggings that feel like a second skin. Made from Nulu fabric — weightless, buttery-soft, and four-way stretch with excellent shape retention. High-rise waistband lies flat and stays put without digging in. No front seam for a smooth, flattering silhouette. Hidden waistband pocket fits a key or card. 25" inseam designed for women 5\'4" and under. Available in 30+ colors. Designed for yoga but loved for everything. Machine washable inside out in cold water. Size 0-20. The most-loved legging in fitness.', ['brand' => 'Lululemon', 'color' => 'True Navy', 'material' => 'Nulu Fabric']],
    ['Allbirds Women\'s Tree Runners', 'Women', 98.00, 'Allbirds Tree Runners are the comfortable, sustainable sneakers made from eucalyptus tree fiber. Breathable, moisture-wicking TENCEL Lyocell upper keeps feet cool and dry. SweetFoam midsole made from sugarcane-based green EVA provides cushioned comfort. Carbon-negative outsole. Machine washable — toss them in cold water and air dry. No-show lace design with reflective eyelets. Removable merino wool insole adds softness. Carbon footprint of 7.6 kg CO2e — among the lowest in the industry. Available in 20+ colors. B Corp certified.', ['brand' => 'Allbirds', 'color' => 'Natural White', 'material' => 'Eucalyptus Fiber']],
    ['The North Face Nuptse Jacket', 'Women', 320.00, 'The North Face 1996 Retro Nuptse Jacket is the iconic puffer that defined a generation. 700-fill recycled down insulation provides exceptional warmth-to-weight ratio. Durable, recycled ripstop nylon shell resists tears and abrasion. Stowable hood tucks into the collar. Secure-zip hand pockets with internal chest pocket. Elastic cuffs and adjustable hem with drawcord. Zip-in compatible with other TNF shells for layered warmth in extreme cold. 600g weight. The Nuptse has been an urban and mountain essential since 1996. Responsible Down Standard certified.', ['brand' => 'The North Face', 'color' => 'TNF Black', 'material' => 'Recycled Nylon/Down']],
    ['Everlane The Cashmere Crew', 'Women', 120.00, 'Everlane Cashmere Crew is the affordable luxury sweater with radical transparency. Grade-A Mongolian cashmere — the finest, longest fibers for pill-resistant softness. Classic crew neck with ribbed cuffs, collar, and hem. Relaxed fit that drapes beautifully over jeans or tucked into a skirt. Available in 15 colors from neutrals to seasonal shades. Machine washable cashmere (yes, really) — just use cold water and a mesh bag. Everlane shows the true cost: materials, labor, transport, and their markup. No traditional retail markup. Ethically sourced.', ['brand' => 'Everlane', 'color' => 'Heather Grey', 'material' => 'Mongolian Cashmere']],

    // ===== Clothing > Kids =====
    ['Mini Boden Fun Jersey Dress', 'Kids', 38.00, 'Mini Boden Fun Jersey Dress makes everyday dressing a joy for girls. Soft cotton jersey with fun prints that kids love — available in florals, stripes, characters, and seasonal designs. A-line swing shape gives room to move, play, and twirl. Long sleeves and a crew neck for year-round wear. Machine washable and durable enough for playgrounds. Pairs perfectly with leggings and boots. Sizes 2-12 years. British-designed with attention to color and detail. Mini Boden donates to children\'s charities with every collection. Mix and match with coordinating accessories.', ['brand' => 'Mini Boden', 'color' => 'Multi Print', 'material' => 'Cotton Jersey']],
    ['Columbia Youth Bugaboo Jacket', 'Kids', 120.00, 'Columbia Bugaboo II Fleece Interchange Jacket is the 3-in-1 system that adapts to any weather. Waterproof, breathable Omni-Tech shell protects from rain and wind. Removable fleece liner provides warmth independently. Zip both together for cold, wet days. Adjustable storm hood, elastic cuffs, and drawcord hem seal out the elements. Reflective details for visibility. Grow system lets you extend sleeve and coat length as your child grows. Sizes XS-XXL (ages 4-18). Machine washable. One jacket, three configurations, years of use.', ['brand' => 'Columbia', 'color' => 'Mountain Red', 'material' => 'Nylon/Fleece']],

    // ===== Shoes > Sneakers =====
    ['Nike Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG', 'Sneakers', 180.00, 'Nike Air Jordan 1 Retro High OG is the sneaker that changed everything. First released in 1985 for Michael Jordan, banned by the NBA, and embraced by counterculture — the AJ1 transcends sport. Premium leather upper with classic colorblocking. Nike Air cushioning in the sole for all-day comfort. Padded collar for ankle support. Rubber cupsole with pivot circle traction. Wings logo debossed on the collar. Each colorway tells a story. From basketball courts to fashion runways, the Jordan 1 remains the most influential sneaker in history.', ['brand' => 'Nike', 'color' => 'Black/White/Sail']],
    ['New Balance 990v6', 'Sneakers', 199.99, 'New Balance 990v6 continues the legacy of the original "dad shoe" that became a fashion icon. Made in USA with premium pigskin suede and mesh upper. FuelCell midsole cushioning is lighter, softer, and more responsive than previous generations. ENCAP support cradle provides medial post stability. Blown rubber outsole with multi-surface traction. Reflective N logo and heel detail. OrthoLite insert for step-in comfort. The 990 series has been the gold standard of American-made athletic footwear since 1982. Available in widths from Narrow to Extra-Wide.', ['brand' => 'New Balance', 'color' => 'Grey', 'material' => 'Suede/Mesh']],
    ['Adidas Ultraboost Light', 'Sneakers', 189.99, 'Adidas Ultraboost Light is the lightest Ultraboost ever — 30% lighter midsole with the same incredible energy return. Light BOOST cushioning uses a new beading process for responsive, bouncy comfort with every step. Continental rubber outsole grips wet and dry surfaces. Primeknit+ upper adapts to foot shape for a sock-like fit with targeted support. Fitcounter molded heel counter for a natural Achilles fit. Torsion System for midfoot integrity. From marathon runners to daily walkers, Ultraboost delivers all-day energy. Made with Parley Ocean Plastic upper.', ['brand' => 'Adidas', 'color' => 'Core Black', 'material' => 'Primeknit+']],
    ['Veja Campo Chromefree Leather', 'Sneakers', 150.00, 'Veja Campo is the sustainable court sneaker that proves style and ethics coexist. ChromeFree leather tanned without heavy metals or harmful chemicals. Wild rubber soles sourced from the Amazon rainforest, supporting local communities and preventing deforestation. V logo made from recycled polyester. Cotton laces from organic farming in Brazil. Lining from recycled plastic bottles. No advertising budget — Veja invests in fair materials and fair wages. Clean, minimalist design works with everything from jeans to chinos. Made in Brazil.', ['brand' => 'Veja', 'color' => 'Extra White/Black', 'material' => 'ChromeFree Leather']],

    // ===== Shoes > Boots =====
    ['Dr. Martens 1460 Smooth Leather', 'Boots', 169.00, 'Dr. Martens 1460 is the original 8-eye boot that has been a symbol of rebellion and self-expression since 1960. Smooth polished leather upper with the iconic yellow welt stitching. Goodyear-welted AirWair bouncing sole provides durability and cushioned comfort. Heel loop for easy pull-on. Lace-up closure with metal eyelets. Break-in period results in a custom fit — these boots mold to your feet over time. Resoleable construction means they can last a lifetime. Made on the original 1460 last. A timeless wardrobe investment.', ['brand' => 'Dr. Martens', 'color' => 'Black Smooth', 'material' => 'Leather']],
    ['Timberland 6-Inch Premium Boot', 'Boots', 198.00, 'Timberland 6-Inch Premium Waterproof Boot is the iconic "yellow boot" born in 1973. Premium full-grain leather upper with seam-sealed waterproof construction. 400g PrimaLoft insulation keeps feet warm without bulk. Anti-fatigue technology with inverted cone geometry returns energy at every step. Padded collar for comfort and support around the ankle. Rubber lug outsole with 15% recycled materials. Steel shank for arch support. ReBOTL fabric lining made from 50% recycled plastic. The boot that built Timberland — from construction sites to city streets.', ['brand' => 'Timberland', 'color' => 'Wheat Nubuck', 'material' => 'Full-Grain Leather']],
    ['Blundstone #585 Chelsea Boot', 'Boots', 219.95, 'Blundstone #585 is the classic rustic Chelsea boot from Tasmania, Australia. Pull-on design with dual elastic side panels — no laces to fuss with. Premium waterproof leather upper. Thermo-urethane outsole (TPU) is heat, oil, and acid resistant. Removable SPS Max Comfort footbed with XRD heel-strike protection. Leather-lined for breathability. Break-in time is minimal — comfortable from the first wear. Versatile enough for light hikes, city walking, and smart casual occasions. Last for years with minimal maintenance. Available in half sizes for a precise fit.', ['brand' => 'Blundstone', 'color' => 'Rustic Brown', 'material' => 'Leather']],

    // ===== Shoes > Sandals =====
    ['Birkenstock Arizona Soft Footbed', 'Sandals', 159.99, 'Birkenstock Arizona is the iconic two-strap sandal with legendary comfort. Anatomically shaped cork-latex footbed supports the natural arch of your foot — orthopedist-designed since 1774. Soft Footbed version adds an extra foam layer for plush cushioning. Oiled nubuck leather upper with adjustable metal pin buckles for a custom fit. Suede-lined footbed for moisture absorption. EVA outsole is flexible, lightweight, and shock-absorbing. Molds to your foot over time for a truly personalized fit. Made in Germany. Available in regular and narrow widths.', ['brand' => 'Birkenstock', 'color' => 'Tobacco Brown', 'material' => 'Oiled Nubuck']],
    ['Teva Original Universal', 'Sandals', 55.00, 'Teva Original Universal is the sport sandal that started the adventure sandal category in 1984. Universal Strapping System adjusts with hook-and-loop for a secure, custom fit. EVA-foam midsole provides lightweight cushioning for all-day wear. Durabrasion rubber outsole grips on wet rocks and trails. Quick-dry webbing straps are made from recycled plastic. Water-friendly construction — wear them in rivers, on beaches, or in the shower. Lightweight at 200g. From Grand Canyon guides to festival-goers, the Original Universal has been the go-anywhere sandal for 40 years.', ['brand' => 'Teva', 'color' => 'Black', 'material' => 'Recycled Webbing']],

    // ===== Shoes > Formal =====
    ['Allen Edmonds Park Avenue Cap-Toe', 'Formal', 395.00, 'Allen Edmonds Park Avenue is the quintessential American dress shoe. Calfskin leather upper with elegant cap-toe design. 360-degree Goodyear welt construction allows resoling — extending the shoe\'s life by decades. Full leather lining and cork-bed insole conform to your foot over time. Single oak-leather sole with a rubber heel tap. Made in Port Washington, Wisconsin using 212 individual steps. Available in sizes 6-16, widths AAA to EEE. The gold standard for boardrooms, weddings, and any occasion that demands your best. Break them in properly and they\'ll last a lifetime.', ['brand' => 'Allen Edmonds', 'color' => 'Black', 'material' => 'Calfskin Leather']],
    ['Cole Haan OriginalGrand Wingtip', 'Formal', 150.00, 'Cole Haan OriginalGrand Wingtip Oxford combines classic dress shoe styling with modern athletic comfort. Stitchlite knit upper provides breathable flexibility with the refined look of wingtip broguing. Grand.OS cushioning technology delivers lightweight comfort — feels more like a sneaker than a dress shoe. EVA midsole for energy return. Rubber outsole pods for traction. Weighs just 280g per shoe. Transitions seamlessly from office to dinner to weekend. The shoe that proved dress shoes don\'t have to hurt. Available in 10+ colorways.', ['brand' => 'Cole Haan', 'color' => 'Black Stitchlite', 'material' => 'Knit/Leather']],

    // ===== More Electronics =====
    ['Apple Watch Ultra 3', 'Fitness', 799.99, 'Apple Watch Ultra 3 is the most rugged and capable Apple Watch for outdoor adventurers. 49mm titanium case with sapphire crystal front. Precision dual-frequency GPS with extended range. Depth gauge and water temperature sensor for recreational diving to 40m. 86dB siren for emergency signaling. Cellular connectivity works even in remote areas with satellite SOS. 72-hour battery life in normal use, 120 hours in Low Power Mode. Action Button for instant access to workouts, waypoints, or shortcuts. Trail Loop, Alpine Loop, and Ocean Band options.', ['brand' => 'Apple', 'color' => 'Natural Titanium']],
    ['Samsung 65" QN90D Neo QLED TV', 'Electronics', 1799.99, 'Samsung QN90D Neo QLED delivers stunning picture quality with Quantum Matrix Technology. Mini LEDs provide precise backlight control for deeper blacks and brighter highlights — up to 2000 nits peak brightness. Neural Quantum Processor 4K AI upscales any content to near-4K quality. 120Hz refresh rate with AMD FreeSync Premium Pro for smooth gaming. Object Tracking Sound+ moves audio to match on-screen action. Samsung Gaming Hub gives instant access to Xbox Cloud Gaming, GeForce NOW, and more. Tizen Smart TV with SmartThings integration.', ['brand' => 'Samsung', 'color' => 'Titan Black']],
    ['Sony PlayStation 5 Pro', 'Electronics', 699.99, 'PlayStation 5 Pro is the most powerful console ever built. Custom AMD GPU with ray tracing acceleration renders photorealistic lighting and reflections in real-time. 16.7 teraflops of GPU power — 67% more than the standard PS5. PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution (PSSR) AI upscaling maintains crisp visuals at higher frame rates. 2TB custom SSD with 12.5 GB/s read speed — virtually no loading screens. 8K output support. DualSense wireless controller with haptic feedback and adaptive triggers. Access to the entire PS5 game library. Wi-Fi 7 for faster downloads.', ['brand' => 'Sony', 'color' => 'White']],
    ['Nintendo Switch 2', 'Electronics', 449.99, 'Nintendo Switch 2 evolves the hybrid gaming concept with a larger 8-inch LCD display and more powerful custom NVIDIA chip. Play on the TV in 4K resolution at 60fps, or take it on the go in handheld mode. Joy-Con 2 controllers feature magnetic attachment, mouse-like sensors, and improved HD Rumble. Backward compatible with all Switch 1 games. New "GameChat" feature for voice chat without a phone app. 256GB internal storage with microSD Express support. USB-C charging. Nintendo Switch Online gives access to NES, SNES, N64, and Game Boy libraries.', ['brand' => 'Nintendo', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Sonos Era 300 Speaker', 'Electronics', 449.00, 'Sonos Era 300 is the spatial audio speaker designed for immersive, room-filling sound. Six optimally placed drivers create a wide, three-dimensional soundstage with Dolby Atmos Music support. Trueplay tuning adapts to your room\'s acoustics — automatically on iOS, or via the built-in mic. Wi-Fi 6 and Bluetooth 5.0 with AirPlay 2. Voice control via Alexa or Sonos Voice Control. Line-in via USB-C adapter. Group with other Sonos speakers for whole-home audio. Stereo pair two Era 300s for ultimate immersion. Sustainable design with 50% recycled plastic. No subscription required.', ['brand' => 'Sonos', 'color' => 'White']],
    ['Kindle Scribe 64GB', 'Electronics', 389.99, 'Amazon Kindle Scribe is the first Kindle you can write on. 10.2-inch glare-free Paperwhite display at 300 PPI. Included Premium Pen feels like writing on paper — no charging or pairing needed. Annotate books, mark up PDFs, and write in built-in notebooks. Active Canvas feature lets your handwritten notes automatically reflow around text when you resize. Front light with warm tone adjustment for comfortable reading day and night. 64GB storage holds thousands of books and notebooks. 12 weeks of battery life. 6.7mm thin, 433g lightweight. Import personal docs via Send to Kindle.', ['brand' => 'Amazon', 'color' => 'Metallic Jade']],
    ['Anker PowerCore 26800mAh', 'Electronics', 65.99, 'Anker PowerCore 26800 is the high-capacity portable charger for travelers and power users. 26,800mAh charges an iPhone 14 over 6 times or a Galaxy S24 over 5 times on a single charge. Dual USB-A output ports deliver 3A total for simultaneous device charging. PowerIQ detects and delivers the optimal charging current for any device. MultiProtect safety system with 11 protection features including short circuit, temperature, and overvoltage protection. Recharges in 6 hours via dual micro-USB input. 475g weight. Includes travel pouch and 2 cables. 18-month warranty.', ['brand' => 'Anker', 'color' => 'Black']],

    // ===== More Home & Kitchen =====
    ['Dyson V15 Detect Absolute', 'Home & Kitchen', 749.99, 'Dyson V15 Detect reveals hidden dust with a precision-engineered green laser on the fluffy cleaner head. Piezo sensor counts and sizes dust particles 15,000 times per second — displaying real-time data on the LCD screen so you know when a surface is truly clean. 240 AW suction power with root cyclone technology that doesn\'t lose suction. 60-minute runtime. HEPA filtration captures 99.99% of particles down to 0.3 microns. Converts from stick to handheld. Hair screw tool with anti-tangle conical brush head. Seven attachments included.', ['brand' => 'Dyson', 'color' => 'Yellow/Nickel']],
    ['iRobot Roomba j9+', 'Home & Kitchen', 899.99, 'iRobot Roomba j9+ is the smart robot vacuum that cleans while you\'re away. PrecisionVision Navigation identifies and avoids obstacles like shoes, cords, and pet waste with a front-facing camera. 3-Stage Cleaning System with dual rubber extractors and 100% stronger suction than the j7+. Automatic dirt disposal into the Clean Base — empties itself for up to 60 days. Smart Mapping learns your home\'s layout and suggests cleaning schedules. Clean by room or zone via app or voice. Ideal for pet owners. Compatible with Alexa and Google Assistant.', ['brand' => 'iRobot', 'color' => 'Graphite']],
    ['Instant Pot Duo Plus 6-Quart', 'Kitchenware', 89.99, 'Instant Pot Duo Plus is the 9-in-1 programmable pressure cooker that replaced seven kitchen appliances. Pressure cooker, slow cooker, rice cooker, steamer, sauté pan, yogurt maker, warmer, sterilizer, and sous vide. Stainless steel 304 inner pot with tri-ply bottom. 15 one-touch smart programs. Cooks food up to 70% faster than traditional methods while preserving nutrients. 10+ safety features including overheat protection and safety lock lid. Dishwasher-safe lid, inner pot, and accessories. Free Instant Pot app with 1000+ recipes. Feeds 4-6 people.', ['brand' => 'Instant Pot', 'color' => 'Stainless Steel']],
    ['Ninja Creami Ice Cream Maker', 'Kitchenware', 199.99, 'Ninja Creami turns frozen ingredients into ice cream, gelato, sorbet, milkshakes, and smoothie bowls in minutes. Creamify Technology breaks down frozen blocks with powerful blades for a smooth, creamy result. Seven one-touch programs for different textures. Create protein-packed ice cream, dairy-free sorbet, or fruit smoothie bowls. Start with any base: dairy, oat milk, coconut, or just fruit. Freeze the pint overnight, process in 2 minutes. Outer bowl dishwasher safe. Includes 3 pint containers with storage lids. Endless customization — add mix-ins after first spin.', ['brand' => 'Ninja', 'color' => 'Silver/Black']],
    ['Weber Spirit II E-310 Gas Grill', 'Home & Kitchen', 519.00, 'Weber Spirit II E-310 is the dependable 3-burner gas grill for backyard cooking. 30,000 BTU-per-hour output across three stainless steel burners with Infinity Ignition for reliable starts. 529 sq in total cooking area (primary + warming rack). Porcelain-enameled cast iron cooking grates provide excellent heat retention and sear marks. GS4 Grilling System with improved burners, Flavorizer bars, and grease management. Built-in lid thermometer. Fold-down side tables. Open cart design. iGrill 3 app-connected thermometer compatible. 10-year limited warranty.', ['brand' => 'Weber', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Nespresso Vertuo Next', 'Kitchenware', 179.00, 'Nespresso Vertuo Next brews both espresso and coffee using Centrifusion technology — the capsule spins at up to 7,000 RPM for a rich crema and optimal extraction. Five cup sizes: espresso (40ml), double espresso (80ml), gran lungo (150ml), mug (230ml), and alto (414ml). Barcode recognition automatically adjusts brewing parameters for each capsule. 54% recycled plastic body. Bluetooth and Wi-Fi connected for firmware updates. One-touch operation — insert capsule, close lever, press button. Heats up in 30 seconds. Auto-off after 2 minutes. Compact footprint for small kitchens.', ['brand' => 'Nespresso', 'color' => 'Matte Black']],
    ['Lodge 12-Inch Cast Iron Skillet', 'Kitchenware', 39.99, 'Lodge 12-inch Cast Iron Skillet is the American kitchen workhorse — seasoned and ready to cook right out of the box. 12-inch cooking surface handles everything from cornbread to steaks to deep-dish pizza. Cast iron retains heat evenly and develops a natural non-stick patina with use. Foundry-seasoned with vegetable oil — 100% natural, no synthetic coatings. Oven safe to any temperature. Works on gas, electric, induction, grill, and campfire. Two pour spouts and an assist handle. Made in South Pittsburgh, Tennessee since 1896. Lasts generations — many 100-year-old Lodges are still cooking today.', ['brand' => 'Lodge', 'color' => 'Black', 'material' => 'Cast Iron']],

    // ===== More Sports =====
    ['Yonex EZONE 98 Tennis Racquet', 'Sports & Outdoors', 249.99, 'Yonex EZONE 98 is the power-oriented racquet used by ATP and WTA tour players. 98 sq in head size with a 16x19 string pattern for spin and power. Isometric head shape expands the sweet spot by 7% compared to conventional frames. VDM (Vibration Dampening Mesh) in the handle absorbs harsh vibrations. 2G-Namd Flex Force graphite generates more flex at impact for a powerful, comfortable response. 305g unstrung weight for a balanced feel between power and control. Head light balance for quick maneuverability at the net.', ['brand' => 'Yonex', 'color' => 'Aqua Night Black']],
    ['Callaway Paradym Ai Smoke Driver', 'Sports & Outdoors', 599.99, 'Callaway Paradym Ai Smoke driver uses artificial intelligence to design the optimal face for maximum distance. Ai Smart Face optimized from 50,000+ real swings — not just robot testing. Jailbreak AI Speed Frame connects the crown and sole for explosive ball speed. Triaxial carbon crown saves weight for a lower CG. 460cc head with adjustable hosel (±2° loft). OptiFit 3 system offers 24 different settings. Speed cartridge in the front of the sole adds 3g of additional mass low and forward. Aldila Ascent shaft options from ultralight to tour-weight.', ['brand' => 'Callaway', 'color' => 'Carbon/Black']],
    ['Hydro Flask 32oz Wide Mouth', 'Sports & Outdoors', 44.95, 'Hydro Flask 32oz Wide Mouth is the insulated water bottle that keeps drinks cold for 24 hours or hot for 12. TempShield double-wall vacuum insulation — no condensation on the outside. 18/8 pro-grade stainless steel won\'t retain or transfer flavors. BPA-free and phthalate-free. Wide mouth fits ice cubes and is easy to clean. Honeycomb insulated cap. Powder-coated Color Last finish resists chipping, peeling, and fading. Lifetime warranty. Compatible with Hydro Flip, Straw, and Wide Mouth Sport Cap accessories.', ['brand' => 'Hydro Flask', 'color' => 'Pacific Blue', 'material' => 'Stainless Steel']],
    ['Manduka PRO Yoga Mat', 'Fitness', 129.00, 'Manduka PRO is the high-performance yoga mat chosen by teachers and serious practitioners worldwide. 6mm thick, high-density cushioning protects joints without sacrificing stability. Closed-cell surface prevents sweat and bacteria from absorbing into the mat. 71-inch length accommodates tall practitioners. 6.8 lbs — heavy enough to stay flat without bunching. Certified OEKO-TEX for chemical safety. Dot-patterned bottom grips any floor surface. Lifetime warranty — Manduka PRO mats last decades with proper care. Break-in period of 15-20 uses develops optimal grip. Made without latex, toxic glues, or phthalates.', ['brand' => 'Manduka', 'color' => 'Black', 'material' => 'PVC']],

    // ===== More diverse products =====
    ['Bose SoundLink Max Portable Speaker', 'Electronics', 399.00, 'Bose SoundLink Max is the biggest, boldest portable speaker from Bose. Dual opposing passive radiators produce deep, powerful bass that fills large outdoor spaces. Stereo Spatial sound provides an immersive listening experience. IP67 waterproof and dustproof — survives pool parties and beach trips. 20-hour battery life. Bluetooth 5.4 with Auracast for sharing audio with unlimited nearby speakers. NFC one-tap pairing. Built-in microphone for calls. USB-C charging. Rope handle for easy carrying. Pair two for stereo. Bose app with customizable EQ.', ['brand' => 'Bose', 'color' => 'Blue Dusk']],
    ['Aesop Resurrection Aromatique Hand Balm', 'Skincare', 33.00, 'Aesop Resurrection Aromatique Hand Balm is the luxurious daily hand moisturizer with a distinctive citrus-woody scent. Formulated with mandarin rind, rosemary leaf, and cedar atlas — creating an aromatic experience with every application. Rapidly absorbed, non-greasy formula provides lasting hydration. Shea butter and cocoa butter deeply nourish dry, overworked hands. Macadamia seed oil softens rough patches. Suitable for all skin types. Cruelty-free and vegan. 75ml aluminum tube with a satisfyingly substantial feel. The scent alone justifies the price — functional luxury.', ['brand' => 'Aesop']],
    ['Peak Design Everyday Backpack 30L', 'Electronics', 289.95, 'Peak Design Everyday Backpack V2 is the versatile camera bag that doesn\'t look like a camera bag. 30L capacity with FlexFold dividers that customize into any configuration for cameras, lenses, laptops, or everyday items. MagLatch top access opens wide with one hand. Dual side-zip access for quick gear grabs without opening the top. Padded laptop/tablet sleeve fits 16" MacBook Pro. External carry straps for tripod, water bottle, or jacket. 100% recycled 400D nylon shell with weatherproof DWR coating. Lifetime warranty. Available in 20L and 30L.', ['brand' => 'Peak Design', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Fellow Stagg EKG Electric Kettle', 'Kitchenware', 195.00, 'Fellow Stagg EKG is the precision pour-over kettle that looks as good as it brews. Variable temperature control from 57-100°C in 1-degree increments — crucial for pour-over coffee extraction. Built-in brew stopwatch on the minimalist LCD display. Precision pour spout designed for a steady, controlled flow rate. Hold toggle maintains temperature for 60 minutes. 900ml capacity. Counterbalanced handle for comfortable, controlled pouring. 1200W quick-heat element. Barista-approved in specialty coffee shops worldwide. Available in matte black, white, copper, and studio editions.', ['brand' => 'Fellow', 'color' => 'Matte Black', 'material' => 'Stainless Steel']],
    ['Moleskine Classic Notebook Large', 'Home & Kitchen', 22.50, 'Moleskine Classic Notebook is the legendary notebook used by artists, writers, and thinkers for over a century. Van Gogh, Hemingway, and Picasso carried Moleskines. Large format (13x21 cm) with 240 ruled pages on ivory-colored 70gsm acid-free paper. Thread-bound for lay-flat writing. Rounded corners resist dog-earing. Elastic closure band. Expandable inner pocket for loose papers. Ribbon bookmark. Hard cover withstands travel in bags and pockets. Available in ruled, plain, dotted, and squared. The original creative companion. Certified B Corporation.', ['brand' => 'Moleskine', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Rogue Fitness Ohio Bar', 'Fitness', 345.00, 'Rogue Ohio Bar is the multipurpose barbell trusted by CrossFit boxes, home gyms, and powerlifting platforms worldwide. 20 kg men\'s bar with 28.5mm shaft diameter. 190,000 PSI tensile strength steel — no permanent bend under heavy loads. Dual knurl marks for Olympic and powerlifting positioning. Medium-depth knurl provides secure grip without tearing hands. Bright zinc shaft with bright zinc sleeves for corrosion resistance. Composite bushings for smooth, reliable spin. Made in Columbus, Ohio. Lifetime warranty against bending and manufacturer defects.', ['brand' => 'Rogue Fitness', 'color' => 'Bright Zinc', 'material' => 'Steel']],
    ['Ember Temperature Control Mug 2', 'Kitchenware', 149.95, 'Ember Mug 2 keeps your coffee at the exact temperature you choose — from 50°C to 62.5°C — from the first sip to the last. Set your preferred temperature in the Ember app and the built-in heating element maintains it for up to 80 minutes on a full charge. Includes charging coaster for all-day warmth at your desk. Auto-sleep detects when empty. IPX7 waterproof — hand wash only. 414ml capacity in a comfortable ceramic-coated stainless steel form. LED indicator ring shows heating status. Works with Apple Health for caffeine tracking.', ['brand' => 'Ember', 'color' => 'Black', 'material' => 'Stainless Steel']],
    ['Bellroy Tokyo Totepack', 'Clothing', 199.00, 'Bellroy Tokyo Totepack converts from a sleek tote to a comfortable backpack with hidden shoulder straps. 15L capacity with a padded laptop compartment for 15" devices. Premium recycled woven fabric with water-resistant finish. Internal organization: phone pocket, pen slots, key clip, and quick-access front pocket. YKK AquaGuard zippers. Magnetic closure for the main compartment. Weighs just 600g. The design lets you switch carry modes without removing contents. Perfect for bike commuters, train riders, and anyone who wants one bag that adapts to the moment. 3-year warranty.', ['brand' => 'Bellroy', 'color' => 'Ranger Green']],

    // ===== More Beauty =====
    ['Drunk Elephant Protini Polypeptide Moisturizer', 'Skincare', 68.00, 'Drunk Elephant Protini Polypeptide Cream is the protein-rich moisturizer that firms, strengthens, and improves skin texture. Signal peptides, growth factors, amino acids, and pygmy waterlily stem cell extract work together to visibly improve skin\'s tone and texture. Soybean folic acid ferment extract and acetyl glutamine support the skin barrier. Free of essential oils, silicones, fragrances, and drying alcohols — the "Suspicious 6" that Drunk Elephant avoids in all products. pH 4.0. Pairs with any Drunk Elephant serum. 50ml pump jar.', ['brand' => 'Drunk Elephant']],
    ['Dyson Supersonic Hair Dryer', 'Haircare', 429.99, 'Dyson Supersonic revolutionized hair drying with a digital motor engineered for fast, focused airflow. V9 digital motor spins at 110,000 RPM — the fastest in any hair dryer. Intelligent heat control measures air temperature 40 times per second to prevent extreme heat damage. Four heat settings, three speed settings, and a cold shot. Five magnetic attachments: smoothing nozzle, styling concentrator, diffuser, gentle air attachment, and flyaway attachment (uses the Coanda effect to hide flyaways). 1600W power. 30% lighter than conventional dryers. Includes storage case with Supersonic.', ['brand' => 'Dyson', 'color' => 'Nickel/Copper']],
    ['Tom Ford Black Orchid Eau de Parfum', 'Beauty & Health', 160.00, 'Tom Ford Black Orchid is the luxurious, dark, and sensual fragrance that redefined modern perfumery. A rich blend of black truffle, ylang ylang, bergamot, and black orchid over a heart of black plum, rum absolute, and lotus wood. Base notes of patchouli, incense, vanilla, vetiver, and sandalwood create a warm, lingering finish. Unisex fragrance with a mysterious, sophisticated character. The iconic dark fluted bottle is as striking as the scent within. 100ml Eau de Parfum. Long-lasting — 8+ hours on skin.', ['brand' => 'Tom Ford']],

    // ===== More diverse =====
    ['Sonos Arc Soundbar', 'Electronics', 899.00, 'Sonos Arc is the premium Dolby Atmos soundbar for cinematic home audio. 11 high-performance drivers — including two upward-firing speakers — create an immersive three-dimensional sound field. Speech enhancement mode makes dialogue crystal clear. Night Sound mode reduces loud effects and boosts quiet sounds for late-night viewing. Trueplay room correction optimizes audio for your space. HDMI eARC connects to your TV with a single cable. AirPlay 2, Bluetooth, and Wi-Fi streaming. Voice control via Alexa or Sonos Voice. Pair with Sub and Era speakers for full surround.', ['brand' => 'Sonos', 'color' => 'Black']],
    ['Therabody TheraFace PRO', 'Tools', 399.00, 'TheraFace PRO is the all-in-one facial health device with percussive therapy, LED light therapy, and microcurrent stimulation. Three interchangeable ring attachments: percussive for facial tension, LED light for skin rejuvenation (red, red + infrared, blue), and microcurrent for muscle toning. Hot and cold ring for temperature therapy. QuietForce Technology operates at near-silent levels. Ergonomic handle designed for facial contours. 3 speed settings for each mode. 90-minute battery. Travel case included. Replaces $500+ in separate skincare devices. Bluetooth-connected with guided routines in the Therabody app.', ['brand' => 'Therabody', 'color' => 'White']],
