    ['Yeti Rambler 20oz Tumbler', 'Sports & Outdoors', 35.00, 'YETI Rambler 20oz Tumbler keeps drinks at the perfect temperature — hot or cold. Double-wall vacuum insulation prevents condensation on the outside. 18/8 kitchen-grade stainless steel construction won\'t retain or transfer flavors. Dishwasher safe. MagSlider Lid uses magnets for a secure, spill-resistant closure. No-sweat design means no coasters needed. Fits most cup holders. BPA-free. Available in 25+ DuraCoat colors that won\'t crack, peel, or fade. Perfect for coffee, smoothies, or cocktails. The daily driver that goes from desk to tailgate. 5-year warranty.', ['brand' => 'YETI', 'color' => 'Navy']],
